# Skill Governance

- Apply a skill only when task intent matches the skill purpose.
- Read the selected skill instructions before implementing changes.
- Do not mention a skill without actually applying its workflow.
- Keep skill-driven output concise and implementation-first.
- Prefer reusable contracts and adapters when skill output adds behavior.
- If requirements are unclear, ask targeted questions before implementation.
